Create a modern, bold, and purpose-driven website for Neev Ventures, a social enterprise focused on empowering rural women entrepreneurs.

Overall Brand Feel

The website should feel warm, confident, contemporary, and impact-focused.
Balance softness and strength — human, inclusive, and mission-led, but not delicate or minimal.
Design should feel like a new-age NGO + startup hybrid.

Color Palette

Use colors inspired directly from the provided logo.

Primary Background

Soft warm beige / sand tone as the main background across the website

Hex inspiration: #F4E6C8, #F6EAD6

Primary Accent Colors

Muted sage blue / teal blue from the logo for buttons, highlights, icons

Olive-gold accents for borders, frames, dividers

Secondary Accents

Terracotta / muted orange for emphasis elements (CTA highlights, section dividers)

Very subtle pink or peach tones only where needed

Text Colors

Dark charcoal or deep muted blue for body text

Avoid pure black; keep it warm and readable

Typography

Use one bold, modern sans-serif font family across the entire website.

Font Characteristics

Rounded but confident

High legibility

Bold weights used generously

Slightly artistic but still professional

Font Usage

Headings: Extra Bold / Bold

Subheadings: Bold

Body text: Medium to Semi-Bold

Quotes or mission lines: Bold + slightly larger size

Typography should feel stronger and bolder than the text shown in the image, while maintaining the same clean aesthetic.

Logo Usage

Place logo prominently in the header

Use logo frame color (olive-gold) as a recurring design element:

Section outlines

Image frames

Card borders

Do not overuse the logo icon; let colors and typography carry the brand

Layout & Design Style

Clean grid layout

Generous spacing

Rounded corners on cards and buttons

Soft shadows (very subtle)

No sharp or aggressive angles

Use abstract shapes inspired by the logo in the background:

Curves

Semi-circles

Overlapping organic forms
All shapes should be very light and low opacity.

Homepage Structure

Hero Section

Large bold headline about empowering rural women

Short mission statement

Primary CTA button (bold blue)

Soft abstract shapes in background

About Neev Ventures

Mission-driven storytelling

Emphasize access, skills, ownership, leadership

What We Do

Financial tools

Product skills

Market access

SHG collaboration
Use icon cards with logo-inspired colors

Impact Section

Numbers, stories, and outcomes

Bold typography

Beige background with blue highlights

Belief Statement
Feature this prominently:
“Empowerment is not charity. It is the power to create, own, and lead.”

Call to Action

Partner with us

Support rural women entrepreneurs

Buttons & UI Elements

Rounded buttons

Bold text

Primary buttons in sage blue

Secondary buttons outlined with olive-gold

Hover effects should be smooth and subtle

Imagery Style

Authentic, real, human

Rural women, craftsmanship, collaboration

Warm lighting

No stock-photo look

Slight beige overlay on images to match brand tone

Footer

Simple and clean

Beige background

Bold headings

Social links styled with logo colors

Final Notes

Keep the website bold, not delicate

Avoid pure white backgrounds

Maintain consistency in color and font throughout

